  • Enclosing class:
    AssetTagCache

    protected static class AssetTagCache.AssetTagCacheKey
extends FileScopeCache.FileScopeCacheKey
    Key object for AssetTagCache. It has 4 properties:
    1. absolute path to a SWC file
    2. library path - relative to the root of the SWC file archive
    3. script name - script in the library
    4. qname - QName of the definition
